 you.\nA.RGUY\n/t-\n\u201er\nst*\nVv\u00bb\u00ab?fr.\nFor that which has passed and gone, let us\nfeel thankful\u2014mayhap we all needed the lesson,\nthat piping time of economy.\nThe New Year is here\u2014let us hail it with joy\n\u2014a return of prosperity\u2014the light of brighter\ndays\u2014hopes of a rosy future\u2014may we merit a\nus in the\npast.\nDoell Bros.\nA Joyou NrVYeai'\nTO YOU AND YOUR NEW YEAR\nMay your New Years Day contain the same\namount of Happiness as ypjir Ghmstmas Day,\nand may each Today in the New Year prove\nHappier and Brighter than its Yesterday\u2014and\neach Tomorrow Brighter and Happier than its\nToday. \u2014Bregenzer.\nHOME HOTEL\n4^9 *M IV rf\nL*\nKt -f-W\nv\u00bb\n\"f\n3 xUt3\nsv\"* \"k^\nrt\nv,\" *V\nMay the New Year hold for you all 3\n'that you desire and bring you life's\nrichest blessings.\nDR. F. W. MAERCKLEIN\nBUSffS HARDWARE\nextends\nCORDIAL GREETINGS\nand every Good Wish for you$%\nduring the Coming Year\n0$jj$k\ni|p\ns.\nISi:\n\u2022Sal\nWUh\n\"f 'Cj,\nsis\n\u2022:kmM","height":"26168","width":"18928"}}
